{"tid":2111983,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華府狙擊中國科企 研禁抖音微信","createTime":"2020-07-17T03:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T03:22:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cb0c95d8f93f852a34b47ce454aab20dcd062bfe","tid":2111983,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:15:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200717/PC7VXH534MSAY4K2NNVEPEORJI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200717%2FPC7VXH534MSAY4K2NNVEPEORJI%2F&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=b7f97481\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200717%2FPC7VXH534MSAY4K2NNVEPEORJI%2F&h=663ea103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200717/PC7VXH534MSAY4K2NNVEPEORJI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n華府狙擊中國科企 研禁抖音微信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DDvStpQJLQbnOAgM7anlMcBS728=/640x409/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ECLNZ365HKEXPQ7NQFV2O23WLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDDvStpQJLQbnOAgM7anlMcBS728%3D%2F640x409%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FECLNZ365HKEXPQ7NQFV2O23WLU.jpg&h=6fb50570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTikTok屢被指將用戶資料「送中」，惹多國忌憚。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n美國對華為窮追猛打之際，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮幕僚長梅多斯（Mark Meadows）表示，TikTok、微信和其他應用程式構成潛在國安風險，尤其是涉及外國敵人大規模收集美國公民資料，美國一批官員正在審視TikTok、微信和其他程式帶來的國安威脅：「我不知道官員有否就採取行動的時間訂立時限，<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">但可以說行動可能會在數周、而非數月內出台</span></span>。」美國國務卿蓬佩奧早前表示美方考慮禁用包括TikTok在內的中國社媒應用程式，美。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美司法部長轟美企「勾結中共」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：解放軍拒撤出山區 中印再陷緊張<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國司法部長巴爾昨接力炮轟中國：「很明顯，中國尋求的不僅僅是加入其他發達工業經濟體的行列，而是完全取代它們。」他批評包括華特迪士尼等荷李活業界，長期屈從於北京的壓力審查電影以「取悅中共」。他又炮轟包括Google、微軟、蘋果等科企，「已經表現出非常願意」與中共勾結合作。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"afc8041a8bc96aaa18c938bb7c3efc1789a29845","tid":2111983,"uid":180302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:16:53.000Z","msg":"打未呀 快啲啦"},{"pid":"92c6b3c2d4542f87088881f3bde034b2c30dd8e8","tid":2111983,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:20:25.000Z","msg":"karma <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eaddf0851c847fe263ab14b17b236aed5787874","tid":2111983,"uid":265839,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:21:17.000Z","msg":"Zoom 都係，ban 鳩埋佢啦"},{"pid":"2f3b346afe317db390b8b5938e761936a1e12f8c","tid":2111983,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:22:25.000Z","msg":"快啦 所有中共social media app都要禁晒"}]}